{"tid":1713912,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如果有暴徒 觀塘牛頭角九龍灣 月台路軌倒成桶油 點算？","createTime":"2019-11-12T22:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:16:26.000Z","uid":222970,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41f7ebb6b5f4104fb5861d70c6cfb0a1f58d4572","tid":1713912,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有暴徒 觀塘牛頭角九龍灣 月台路軌倒成桶油，咁要清幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xii0DtA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXii0DtA.jpg&h=8a325b30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVWJBff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVWJBff.jpg&h=6421f2ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qqLVsmW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqqLVsmW.jpg&h=0f6f0c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】石硤尾龍翔道昨午二時許發生漏油事件，長達二十米油迹遺留西行中線，警員需封鎖三條行車線由工人鋪上木糠「吸油」。警員在路旁撿獲一個壓至變形食油鐵罐，疑是罪魁禍首。事件擾攘一個半小時，工人趕及在下班時間前洗淨馬路，其間警方封閉龍翔道西行三條行車線，車龍延伸一公里。警方估計有運送食油貨車駛經上址，其中一罐食油跌下馬路遭車輛輾爆導致食油四溢。"},{"pid":"55f02b724bb0111df7d5affa5d103797fc23dd33","tid":1713912,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:03:41.000Z","msg":"美好風景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdoDqaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdoDqaS.jpg&h=ed7ca6a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"357d391b785aa64133a36160c53e3fe39093d29e","tid":1713912,"uid":58164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T22:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src